data.value:
Close to both Arc de Triomphe and Palais des Congrès de Paris, Mode Paris Aparthotel is situated in Paris and has a fitness room and garden. This 4-star aparthotel offers a 24-hour front desk and a lift. Boasting family rooms, this property also provides guests with a sun terrace.
At the aparthotel, every unit is equipped with a wardrobe and a flat-screen TV. Featuring a private bathroom with a shower and a hair dryer, units at the aparthotel also boast free WiFi. All units will provide guests with a microwave.
There is a coffee shop and lounge. Eiffel Tower is 2.3 km from the aparthotel, while Musée de l'Orangerie is 3.3 km from the property. The nearest airport is Paris - Orly Airport, 22 km from Mode Paris Aparthotel.
